description:
This is a 12 minute workout called 'High Rhythm HIIT Row' from the channel Mike Dostal.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Nightclub Workout and The Firestarter vibe.
The The Nightclub Workout vibe means Lights down, music up, full-body euphoria. This is especially good for When you want to move like no oneâ€™s watching and feel amazing. The The Firestarter vibe means Fast, explosive, and electrifying. Short but devastating. This is especially good for When you only have 10-20 minutes but want to give 1000%..
The technique difficulty is Advanced.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Reach rhythms 28 through 34 during 45" and 30" intervals with Mike to a hip-hop station.
